{
  "_meta": {
    "version": 3,
    "notes": "Unified multi-storey Substructure: foundation types (Pad / Strip / Raft / Pile) live as sub-items under shared headings (Excavation, Filling, Concrete, Formwork, etc.), so a single project that mixes foundations renders all relevant rows. Empty items/elements/bills are skipped at export time. Rates come from each item.rate as saved in the BoQ view — no hard-coded rates. Lookups use case-insensitive AND-of-words matching against an item's description / takeoffLine / materialName / type. Em-dash and hyphen are both handled at lookup time."
  },

